**4. Key Code Changes**
   - High-level summary of code modifications
   - New files added
   - Existing files modified
   - Files removed (if any)
   - Focus on significant changes, not every line

**5. Testing Notes**
   - How the implementation was validated
   - Test cases executed
   - Test results
   - Any special testing considerations

**Complete PR Description Template:**

```markdown
## Azure DevOps Ticket ID
Ticket ID: #<ticket-id>

## Summary of Implementation
<Brief 2-4 sentence overview of what was implemented and why>

## Modified Services

### Primary Service(s)
- **service-name** - <brief description of changes>

### Secondary Service(s)
- **service-name** - <brief description of changes> (if applicable)

## Key Code Changes

### New Files
- `path/to/new-file.ts` - <purpose of new file>

